headline: What New Analyst Moves Mean for Fair Isaac's Evolving Valuation Story
summary: Fair Isaac stock has seen a marginal decline in its consensus analyst price target, slipping by less than one dollar from $2,016.60 to $2,016.44. This reflects a mix of optimism around product innovation and revenue growth, as well as caution in response to recent earnings and shifting industry dynamics.
